        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="参考资料"><a href="#参考资料" class="headerlink" title="参考资料"></a>参考资料</h2><h3 id="B站教程"><a href="#B站教程" class="headerlink" title="B站教程"></a>B站教程</h3><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=242739348&amp;bvid=BV1je41147Ma&amp;cid=175533032&amp;page=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"> </iframe><p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1ci4y1L7j8?p=2">Typora+PicGo+阿里云OSS实现云笔记|Typora上传图片</a></p><p><img src="https://dandelionstar.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109214748448.png" alt="image-20211109214748448"></p><h3 id="博客地址"><a href="#博客地址" class="headerlink" title="博客地址"></a>博客地址</h3><p><a href="https://blog.17lai.site/posts/40300608/">Docker 版 hexo 环境一键部署</a></p><p><img src="https://dandelionstar.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20211110011246.png"></p><p><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">hexo教程</a></p><p><img src="https://dandelionstar.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109215812669.png"></p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/jspnetcn/article/details/104111651">视频博客教程-基于Hexo的matery主题搭建博客并优化</a></p><p><img src="https://dandelionstar.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109214224625.png"></p><p><a href="https://github.com/blinkfox/hexo-theme-matery/blob/develop/README_CN.md">GitHub上hexo-theme-matery主题博客地址</a></p><p><img src="https://dandelionstar.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109200303248.png"></p><p><a href="https://gitee.com/byh88/hexo-theme-matery">国内hexo-theme-matery主题博客地址</a></p><p><img src="https://dandelionstar.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109213819734.png"></p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42395140/article/details/111642339">Typora中的emoji表情</a></p><p><img src="https://dandelionstar.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109214108110.png"></p><h3 id="演示示例"><a href="#演示示例" class="headerlink" title="演示示例"></a>演示示例</h3><p><a href="http://blinkfox.com/">闪烁之狐-国内hexo-theme-matery访问实例</a></p><p><img src="https:/